		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#searchInput">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content mw-content-ltr" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">1859 effort by abolitionist John Brown to initiate an armed slave revolt in Southern states</div>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">See also: <a href="/wiki/John_Brown%27s_raiders" title="John Brown&#39;s raiders">John Brown's raiders</a></div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r963460841">@media all and (min-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .desktop-float-right{box-sizing:border-box;float:right;clear:right}}.mw-parser-output .infobox.vevent .status>p:first-child{margin:0}</style><table class="infobox vevent" style="width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;"><tbody><tr><th class="summary" colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">John Brown's raid on Harpers Ferry</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="background-color:#DCDCDC;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;">Part of the <a href="/wiki/Origins_of_the_American_Civil_War" title="Origins of the American Civil War">Origins of the American Civil War</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;line-height:1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:HWFireHouseBrown.jpg" class="image"><img alt="HWFireHouseBrown.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/42/HWFireHouseBrown.jpg/300px-HWFireHouseBrown.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="203" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/42/HWFireHouseBrown.jpg/450px-HWFireHouseBrown.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/42/HWFireHouseBrown.jpg/600px-HWFireHouseBrown.jpg 2x" data-file-width="620" data-file-height="420" /></a><br /><i><a href="/wiki/Harper%27s_Weekly" title="Harper&#39;s Weekly">Harper's Weekly</a></i> illustration of U.S. Marines attacking John Brown's "Fort"</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2"><table style="width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0;display:inline-table"><tbody><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Date</th><td>October 16–18, 1859</td></tr><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Location</th><td><div class="location"><a href="/wiki/Harpers_Ferry" class="mw-redirect" title="Harpers Ferry">Harpers Ferry</a>, <a href="/wiki/Virginia" title="Virginia">Virginia</a><br /><span style="font-size:85%;">(now <a href="/wiki/West_Virginia" title="West Virginia">West Virgin