<li id="cite_note-North-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-7"><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-8"><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-9"><sup><i><b>j</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-North_5-10"><sup><i><b>k</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1067248974"/><cite id="CITEREFGreen&#91;e&#93;1885" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Israel_Greene" title="Israel Greene">Green[e], Israel</a> (December 1885). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uc1.b4806405&amp;view=1up&amp;seq=572&amp;q1=John%20brown">"The Capture of John Brown"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/North_American_Review" title="North American Review">North American Review</a></i>: 564–569. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210123181618/https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uc1.b4806405&amp;view=1up&amp;seq=572&amp;q1=John%20brown">Archived</a> from the original on January 23, 2021<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">January 16,</span> 2021</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=North+American+Review&amp;rft.atitle=The+Capture+of+John+Brown&amp;rft.pages=564-569&amp;rft.date=1885-12&amp;rft.aulast=Green%5Be%5D&amp;rft.aufirst=Israel&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbabel.hathitrust.org%2Fcgi%2Fpt%3Fid%3Duc1.b4806405%